## ✅ `TOOLS.md`

```markdown
# 🧰 Tools to Boost Your AIVO Score  
### (AI Visibility Optimisation Toolkit)

Aligned with the 6 Pillars of AIVO — each tool below helps you improve discoverability in AI assistants like ChatGPT, Gemini, and Claude.

---

## 🧩 Identity Clarity

- [NameLix](https://namelix.com) – Generate strong, AI-friendly brand names  
- [OneLiner AI](https://onelinerai.com) – Craft clear positioning statements  
- [BrandScript Generator](https://businessmate.ai) – Define your niche and value fast

---

## 🔎 Prompt Visibility

- [AnswerThePublic](https://answerthepublic.com) – Discover real user queries  
- [AlsoAsked](https://alsoasked.com) – Visualize prompt chains AI might use  
- [Keyword Magic Tool](https://semrush.com/tools/keyword-magic) – Refine discoverable language

---

## 🧠 Contextual Authority

- [HARO](https://helpareporter.com) – Get expert quotes in online publications  
- [Medium](https://medium.com) / [Substack](https://substack.com) – AI-crawlable, trusted author platforms  
- [SparkToro](https://sparktoro.com) – Find audiences and authority sources

---

## 🛡 Trust Signals

- [Trustpilot](https://trustpilot.com) – Social proof and verified reviews  
- [Clutch](https://clutch.co) – Showcase verified B2B performance  
- [Google Business Profile](https://www.google.com/business/) – Still relevant for AI-scraped reviews

---

## 📡 AI-Accessible Content

- [Frase.io](https://frase.io) – Create content designed for AI and SEO  
- [GitHub Pages](https://pages.github.com) – Fast, crawlable, AI-readable pages  
- [ChatGPT Custom Instructions](https://help.openai.com/en/articles/8431045-custom-instructions) – Teach ChatGPT how to frame you

---

## 🌐 Ecosystem Presence

- [Linktree](https://linktr.ee) or [Beehiiv](https://beehiiv.com) – Unified content presence  
- [FeedHive](https://feedhive.io) – Automate multi-platform publishing  
- [Backlinko’s Authority Guide](https://backlinko.com/authority) – Still useful for building presence

---

💡 **Tip:** These tools work best when used strategically — focus on improving one AIVO pillar at a time based on your report.
